<body>
    <p class="p1">This is the first paragraph with left alignment and Arial font.</p>
    <p class="p2">This is the second paragraph with center alignment and Georgia font.</p>
    <p class="p3">This is the third paragraph with right alignment and Courier New font.</p>
    <p class="p4">This is the fourth paragraph with justify alignment and Verdana font. Adding more text to demonstrate text justification effect properly.</p>
    <p class="p5">This is the fifth paragraph with center alignment and Trebuchet MS font.</p>
